# Brotli-precompressed web export files. Regenerated by deploy.sh on
# the VPS post-import; Caddy's file_server.precompressed serves them
# when the client supports `Accept-Encoding: br`. ~3MB each, no value
# in carrying them in git.
docs/*.br

# Internal working state — not for public repo.
# Exception: codexreview.md is tracked so the scheduled review-fix routine
# (remote agent, clones from GitHub) can read the outstanding P0/P1/P2 list.
# todo.md / test.md stay local-only.
.agent/*
!.agent/codexreview.md
fix-local-camera-current.patch
builds/
